lines.text:
[singing to the tune of "Home on the Range"]
Oh, give me a home / Where da billionaires roam / An' de oil and da cattlemen play / Wit dere gushin' oil wells / An' super hotels / An' count up dere money all day / An' dat ain't hay.
A birthday cake! Now who coulda knowed it was my birthday? Especially when it t'ain't.
